            bindings = <
                &kp J         &kp C            &kp Y                &kp F         &kp K         &kp Z             &kp W         &kp U                 &key_repeat  &kp Q
                &hml LCTRL R  &hml LEFT_ALT S  &hml LEFT_COMMAND T  &hml LSHFT H  &kp P         &kp M             &hmr RSHFT N  &hmr RIGHT_COMMAND I  &hmr RALT A  &hmr RCTRL O
&kp UNDERSCORE  &kp X         &kp V            &kp G                &lt 1 D       &kp B         &kp SINGLE_QUOTE  &kp L         &kp COMMA             &kp DOT      &kp FSLH      &kp Q
                                               &kp TAB              &lt 2 E       &lt 3 BSPC    &lt 4 RETURN      &lt 5 SPACE   &lt 0 ESCAPE
            >;
